    • Constructor Detail

      • PbcCompileBuilder

        @DataBoundConstructor
public PbcCompileBuilder(String execName,
                                                String pbcCompileName,
                                                String cmdLineArgs,
                                                boolean continueOnBuildFailure,
                                                boolean unstableIfWarnings)
        When this builder is created in the project configuration step, the builder object will be created from the strings below.
        Parameters:
        execName - The PBC utility file name
        pbcCompileName - The PowerBuilder logical name
        cmdLineArgs - Whitespace separated list of command line arguments for pbc190.exe
        continueOnBuildFailure - If true, job will continue despite pbc190.exe build failure
        unstableIfWarnings - If true, job will be unstable if there are warnings
